      <ab type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">The night photograph shows the front of the ‘Lifka’ cinema in Subotica with its entrance door open. The cinema announces a film starring Greta Garbo. It is or has been raining. A street lamp in front of the cinema is on.</ab>
      <ab subtype="comment" type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">The cinema’s owner, Aleksandar Lifka (1880–1952), was a cinematographer.</ab>
